profile.primary_concern: navigating the complexities of starting PrEP after undergoing cancer treatment

context: The user is a 35-year-old Tanzanian woman who has recently completed her cancer treatment. While she feels hopeful about her health, she also grapples with anxiety about resuming her sexual health and the potential stigma associated with PrEP.
